ORDER
PER CURIAM:
AND NOW, this 20th day of May, 1999, upon consideration of the Report and Recommendations of the Disciplinary Board dated March 26,1999, it is hereby
ORDERED that E. BRANDT BYTHROW, be subjected to PUBLIC CENSURE by the Supreme Court.
It is further ORDERED that respondent shall pay costs to the Disciplinary Board pursuant to Rule 208(g), Pa.R.D.E.
